@startuml PY-001 Sequence Diagram — Lesson Page Data Flow

title PY-001: Markdown File → Rendered Lesson Page

actor Learner
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "Next.js\n(getStaticProps)" as GSP
participant "/content/lessons/\n[slug].md" as MD

== Page Load ==

Learner -> Browser : navigates to /lessons/[slug]
Browser -> GSP : request page props
GSP -> MD : read file from disk
MD --> GSP : raw markdown string
GSP -> GSP : parse frontmatter\n(title, slug, codeExample)
GSP -> GSP : render markdown body\nto HTML (remark/rehype)
GSP --> Browser : { title, bodyHtml, codeExample }

== Render ==

Browser -> Browser : render LessonHeader (title)
Browser -> Browser : render LessonBody (explanation HTML)
Browser -> Browser : render CodeExample\n(syntax-highlighted)
Browser -> Browser : render TryItButton

Browser --> Learner : lesson page displayed\n(target: < 2 seconds)

== Interaction ==

Learner -> Browser : clicks "Try it"
Browser --> Learner : navigates to /exercises/[slug]

@enduml
